Package database

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatabaseOperation<I>
    Abstract representation of an operation to add or modify a database item.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppointmentDao
    DAO providing read/write access to appointments in the database, which it represents in the application as instances of Appointment.
    AppointmentDao.MonthTypeCount
    POJO for objects returned by getMonthTypeCounts() for the report of appointment counts by appointment month and type.
    ContactCache
    Cache of contacts pulled from the database.
    CountryCache
    Cache of countries pulled from the database.
    CustomerDao
    DAO providing read/write access to customers in the database, which it represents in the application as instances of Customer.
    CustomerDao.CountryDivisionCount
    POJO for objects returned by getCountryDivisionCounts() for the report of customer counts by customer country and "first level division".
    Database
    Class representing the database and managing connections to the database.
    DivisionCache
    Cache of country "first level divisions" pulled from the database.
    LookupCache<I>
    Base class for caches of database items, used for lookups in the application.
    ReadWriteDao<I extends WithID>
    Base class of DAOs that provide read and write access to a class of items in the database.
    UserDao
    DAO providing access to users in the database.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DatabaseException
    Exception representing an application-sanitized database error, including a user-readable message for explanation.
